# Architecture Plan

## Stack

- Backend: Rust, Axum, Tokio, Serde, SQLx, Postgres, Tracing, tower-http
- Frontend: React, Vite, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, React Router, Zustand, React Hook Form
- Infra: Docker, docker-compose, nginx for frontend static serving
- Auth: password hashing with Argon2, JWT access tokens, bearer auth middleware
- Testing: Rust integration tests against test database, Vitest + Testing Library for frontend

