## Suggested Implementation Order Notes

- Land issue 14 earlier than its numeric position if issue sequencing is flexible; error shape stabilization reduces rework.
- Define auth response and todo response schemas before frontend issue 15 to avoid duplicated contract fixes.
- Keep migrations additive and versioned under `backend/migrations/`.
- Reserve README completion for issue 30, but keep `.plan` as the working architecture source until then.
